00:21:46,167 --> 00:21:48,033
I love you, too.

447
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:51,667
What's the deal with the cats?

448
00:21:51,701 --> 00:21:53,400
What do you mean "What's
the deal with the cats"?

449
00:21:53,434 --> 00:21:54,767
They're cats.
Don't you like cats?

450
00:21:54,801 --> 00:21:56,334
Not really.

451
00:21:56,367 --> 00:21:58,167
But I guess you do, huh?

452
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,833
I'm allergic, actually.

453
00:21:59,866 --> 00:22:02,167
What? Then how come
you got so many?

454
00:22:02,200 --> 00:22:04,634
I mean,hadso many.

455
00:22:04,667 --> 00:22:06,500
You ever been
in love, Vincent?

456
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:10,334
I don't know.

457
00:22:10,367 --> 00:22:12,300
Given the events of
the past few days,

458
00:22:12,334 --> 00:22:14,167
and, uh, given
the circumstances

459
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:16,000
of my present condition,

460
00:22:16,033 --> 00:22:17,900
I have to say I would like

461
00:22:17,933 --> 00:22:20,500
to think about that
before I answer. Why?

462
00:22:27,734 --> 00:22:29,701
Her?

463
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:33,300
Looks like
she had a party.

464
00:22:33,334 --> 00:22:34,866
She's got a lot
to celebrate.

465
00:22:34,900 --> 00:22:37,634
She just came
into a lot of money.

466
00:22:37,667 --> 00:22:39,966
Good for her.
Yup.

467
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:42,634
Left her everything I had.

468
00:22:42,667 --> 00:22:45,133
I don't get it.

469
00:22:45,167 --> 00:22:46,900
What's not to get?
Look at her.

470
00:22:46,933 --> 00:22:49,833
Okay, but she's alive,

471
00:22:49,866 --> 00:22:52,866
and you're kind
of indisposed.

472
00:22:55,966 --> 00:22:57,966
Are you trying to tell
me that she may have had

473
00:22:58,000 --> 00:22:59,734
something to do
with your...

474
00:22:59,767 --> 00:23:01,367
untimely passing?

475
00:23:02,866 --> 00:23:05,000
It wasn't untimely, Vincent.

476
00:23:05,033 --> 00:23:07,900
It was precisely timed.
It was perfectly timed.

477
00:23:08,966 --> 00:23:10,667
Wait a second.

478
00:23:10,701 --> 00:23:12,734
Are you trying
to tell me that she's
the one who shot you?

479
00:23:13,801 --> 00:23:15,167
You want to hear
the whole story?

480
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,467
