481
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:18,067
Okay.

482
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:21,833
Hang on a second.

483
00:23:21,866 --> 00:23:23,600
I think somebody else is here.

484
00:23:23,634 --> 00:23:25,634
Somebody is listening to us.

485
00:23:28,100 --> 00:23:29,600
It's you, isn't it?

486
00:23:29,634 --> 00:23:31,801
Nobody invited you here.

487
00:23:31,833 --> 00:23:33,300
Wake up!

488
00:23:33,334 --> 00:23:34,801
Did you hear me?

489
00:23:34,833 --> 00:23:37,133
I said "Wake up." Wake up!

490
00:23:37,167 --> 00:23:41,133
Get your head
out of my... death.

491
00:23:41,167 --> 00:23:44,300
You want me to give you
a bad dream?

492
00:23:44,334 --> 00:23:46,734
Okay. You asked for it.

493
00:23:59,667 --> 00:24:02,167
That is so not fair.

494
00:24:06,866 --> 00:24:08,966
Morgan Turley was in
love with the cat lady.

495
00:24:09,000 --> 00:24:11,200
Cadence Bixby?

496
00:24:11,233 --> 00:24:13,033
When I heard about
that million dollars

497
00:24:13,067 --> 00:24:14,667
he left her, I had a hunch
he might have been

498
00:24:14,701 --> 00:24:16,300
