499
00:24:16,334 --> 00:24:18,233
I think he overplayed
his hand though.

500
00:24:18,267 --> 00:24:19,400
It's kind of tough
to close the deal

501
00:24:19,434 --> 00:24:20,767
from where he is,
don't you think?

502
00:24:20,801 --> 00:24:22,167
I think she may have
seduced him, talked him

503
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:24,267
into getting that ridiculous
life insurance policy,

504
00:24:24,300 --> 00:24:25,767
and then killed him.

505
00:24:25,801 --> 00:24:27,267
Can we talk to her?

506
00:24:30,801 --> 00:24:32,434
Ms. Bixby?

507
00:24:32,467 --> 00:24:35,000
I'm District
Attorney Devalos.

508
00:24:35,033 --> 00:24:37,133
This is Allison Dubois.

509
00:24:37,167 --> 00:24:38,467
Of course, you
already know

510
00:24:38,500 --> 00:24:39,900
Detective Scanlon.
We very much

511
00:24:39,933 --> 00:24:41,667
appreciate you coming
down to speak with us.

512
00:24:41,701 --> 00:24:42,767
Now you've gone too far.

513
00:24:42,801 --> 00:24:44,933
This woman had nothing
to do with anything.

514
00:24:44,966 --> 00:24:46,267
Your assistant on the phone
said you wanted

515
00:24:46,300 --> 00:24:47,866
to talk to me about what
